{"tid":2027002,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HTC 搶先發表 AirPods 黑色款「HTC U Ear」兩大特色搶風頭","createTime":"2020-05-21T09:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T12:14:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"0838c9f93e56dde9bdfd6e3d3d65f0144b6aa914","tid":2027002,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"自從蘋果 AirPods 藍牙真無線耳機（TWS）市場熱賣後，隨後三星、華為、小米、OPPO、ASUS、realme 等 Android 手機廠商也都開始推出，不過似乎大多外型就像是參考 AirPods 而推出設計，直到最近 HTC （宏達電）也推出首款藍牙耳機，並且將此產品命名為「HTC U Ear」，不過外型上似乎神似 AirPods ，更是引起多數人討論。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/htc-u-ear-mimicry-airpods-1140x641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fhtc-u-ear-mimicry-airpods-1140x641.jpg&h=4b8daa78&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n從認證文件內提供的資料看來， HTC U Ear 與蘋果 AirPods 的外型極為相似，同樣都是以光滑亮色系外型來設計，另外在耳機其中一端也有突出設計和長條形耳機主體，外觀遠看相似感達到 90%，設計也與 realme Buds Air 和 華為 FreeBuds 3 略同 ，只不過 HTC U Ear 差異在於耳機開孔和充電端至位於耳機測端非末端，另外還採用黑色系設計。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/htc-u-ear-mimicry-airpods\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fhtc-u-ear-mimicry-airpods&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=649babbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/htc-u-ear-mimicry-airpods</a>"},{"pid":"534a21c57f60909ad1612d5c8e0959d4b5a114dd","tid":2027002,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"從外觀和充電盒設計上，也讓 HTC U Ear 比起 AirPods 更有不少特色，例如：<br />\n<br />\nAirPods 到至今尚未有黑色款式，更讓多對手可以透過其他顏色搶佔市場，不排除 HTC U Ear 除了會推出黑色款外，還會有更多顏色選擇。<br />\n<br />\n充電盒部分則是採用 USB Type-C 充電，AirPods 到現在還是採用自家的 Lightning 接口。<br />\n<br />\nHTC U Ear 充電盒也是採用類似貝殼掀蓋式設計，能夠讓耳機直接平躺方式充電，USB Type-C 充電孔也位於充電盒底端，外型也稍微與之前 AirPods Pro Lite 概念圖片有點類似。"},{"pid":"12328894166c6d358ecae3108b530cdeb90bb9ae","tid":2027002,"uid":127905,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"仲未執架咩<br />\n之前已經講到要賣大廈"},{"pid":"721f3798bb4c23ab3962476e0989e61b724b070c","tid":2027002,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"隻黑AirPod 幾特別呀，apple store 幾時有得賣？"},{"pid":"f9666d79820f0f99eaa6937782b6e4ebe4c9b777","tid":2027002,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/htc-u-ear-vs-airpods-1140x641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fhtc-u-ear-vs-airpods-1140x641.jpg&h=1aa9df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/htc-u-ear-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fhtc-u-ear-1.jpg&h=2fa0e2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/htc-u-ear-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fhtc-u-ear-3.jpg&h=6d85e5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/htc-u-ear-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fhtc-u-ear-2.jpg&h=a12fe523&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98ae76908808de13a50785c29e92fed2ae214d53","tid":2027002,"uid":1130,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:31:14.000Z","msg":"help this company"},{"pid":"74567e945ab0ab3884d7c3417bab67f632bb674d","tid":2027002,"uid":140738,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會被告抄design <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw隻黑色麻麻地好睇"},{"pid":"706b3b9d4ddbe5ab02c0d2894efd0b1c72543ccb","tid":2027002,